ollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/abc-extreme-makeover-home-edition-kardashians-267201 |title=The Kardashians Throw Anti-Bullying Rally With Demi Lovato on 'Extreme Makeover: Home Edition' (Video) |magazine=Hollywood Reporter |date=November 29, 2011 |accessdate=June 29, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2012\n| ''[[Punk'd]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"[[Nick Cannon]]\"{{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| ''[[2012 Teen Choice Awards|Teen Choice Awards]]''\n| Herself\n| Co-hosted with [[Kevin McHale (actor)|Kevin McHale]]{{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| ''[[This Is How I Made It]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Demi Lovato and [[B.o.B]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2558324/this-is-how-i-made-it-trailer/|title=Demi Lovato, Ashley Rickards Reveal 'This Is How I Made It'|date=September 28, 2012|accessdate=January 4, 2018|work=MTV}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2012\u20132013\n| ''[[The X Factor (American TV series)|The X Factor]]''\n| Judge / Mentor\n| [[The X Factor (American season 2)|season 2]]\u2013[[The X Factor (American season 3)|3]]\n|-\n| 2013\u20132014\n| ''[[Glee (TV series)|Glee]]''\n| Dani\n| Recurring role ([[Glee (season 5)|season 5]]); 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Matador (American TV series)|Matador]]''\n| Party Guest\n| Episode: \"Quid Go Pro\" (uncredited){{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2015\n| ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"Divine Inspiration\"{{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| ''[[From Dusk Till Dawn: The Series]]''\n| Maia\n| Episodes: \"There Will Be Blood\" and \"Santa Sangre\"{{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| ''[[We Day]]''\n| Host\n| Television special ([[We Day#2015|10th edition]])\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Victoria's Secret Swim Special]]''\n| Herself / Musical Guest\n| Television special{{Citation needed|date=August 2019}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2017\n| ''[[One Love Manchester]]''\n| Herself\n| Television special\n|-\n| ''[[Project Runway]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode: \"We